---
title: BeaconLink Workflow State Machine
---

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    %% =====================================================
    %% Workflow Creation
    %% =====================================================

    [*] --> Created

    Created : Workflow Requested
    Created : Workflow ID Assigned
    Created : Metadata Persisted

    Created --> Initializing

    %% =====================================================
    %% Initialization
    %% =====================================================

    Initializing : Load Workflow Definition
    Initializing : Validate Parameters
    Initializing : Initialize Context
    Initializing : Allocate Resources

    Initializing --> Validating

    Validating : Validate Workflow Schema
    Validating : Validate Dependencies
    Validating : Validate Permissions

    Validating --> Planning : Validation Successful
    Validating --> Failed : Validation Failed

    %% =====================================================
    %% Planning
    %% =====================================================

    Planning : Build Execution Graph
    Planning : Resolve Task Dependencies
    Planning : Create Execution Stages
    Planning : Compute Parallel Tasks

    Planning --> Scheduling

    Scheduling : Select Execution Targets
    Scheduling : Reserve Agent Capacity
    Scheduling : Apply Placement Policies

    Scheduling --> Queued : Resources Reserved
    Scheduling --> Waiting : Capacity Unavailable

    Waiting : Await Available Resources

    Waiting --> Scheduling : Capacity Available
    Waiting --> Cancelled : Cancellation Requested

    %% =====================================================
    %% Execution Lifecycle
    %% =====================================================

    Queued : Await Execution Slot

    Queued --> Running

    state Running {

        [*] --> StageStarting

        StageStarting : Initialize Stage
        StageStarting : Publish StageStarted Event

        StageStarting --> ExecutingTasks

        state ExecutingTasks {

            [*] --> Dispatching

            Dispatching : Send Tasks to Agents
            Dispatching : Create Execution Context

            Dispatching --> AwaitingResults

            AwaitingResults : Wait for Task Completion
            AwaitingResults : Aggregate Results

            AwaitingResults --> Dispatching : Additional Tasks
            AwaitingResults --> [*] : Stage Complete

        }

        ExecutingTasks --> StageVerification

        StageVerification : Verify Stage Completion
        StageVerification : Validate Outputs

        StageVerification --> StageCompleted : Successful
        StageVerification --> Retrying : Recoverable Failure
        StageVerification --> Rollback : Critical Failure

        StageCompleted : Publish StageCompleted Event

        StageCompleted --> StageStarting : Next Stage
        StageCompleted --> WorkflowCompleted : Final Stage

        Retrying : Retry Failed Tasks

        Retrying --> ExecutingTasks
        Retrying --> Rollback : Retry Limit Exceeded

        Rollback : Execute Compensation Actions
        Rollback : Restore Previous State

        Rollback --> WorkflowRolledBack
        Rollback --> WorkflowFailed

        WorkflowCompleted : All Stages Executed

        WorkflowCompleted --> [*]

        WorkflowRolledBack : Rollback Successful

        WorkflowRolledBack --> [*]

        WorkflowFailed : Execution Failed

        WorkflowFailed --> [*]

    }

    %% =====================================================
    %% Completion
    %% =====================================================

    Running --> Completed

    Completed : Workflow Successful
    Completed : Publish Completion Event
    Completed : Persist Final State

    Completed --> Archived

    Archived : Immutable Execution History

    Archived --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Pause / Resume
    %% =====================================================

    Running --> Paused : Pause Requested

    Paused : Suspend Task Dispatch
    Paused : Preserve Execution Context

    Paused --> Running : Resume Requested
    Paused --> Cancelled : Cancel Requested

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Handling
    %% =====================================================

    Failed : Workflow Initialization Failed
    Failed : Await Operator Action

    Failed --> Planning : Retry Workflow
    Failed --> Cancelled : Cancel Requested

    Cancelled : Workflow Cancelled
    Cancelled : Cleanup Resources

    Cancelled --> Archived

    %% =====================================================
    %% Timeout Handling
    %% =====================================================

    Running --> TimedOut : Execution Timeout

    TimedOut : Stop Active Tasks
    TimedOut : Publish Timeout Event

    TimedOut --> RollbackPending

    RollbackPending : Await Rollback Decision

    RollbackPending --> Running : Continue Execution
    RollbackPending --> Cancelled : Abort Workflow

    %% =====================================================
    %% Global Transitions
    %% =====================================================

    Running --> Failed : Internal Engine Failure
    Planning --> Failed : Planning Failure
    Scheduling --> Failed : Scheduler Failure
    Queued --> Failed : Queue Failure
    Initializing --> Failed : Initialization Failure